    "The emergence of advanced algorithms has significantly enhanced our understanding of tumorigenesis.",
    "For instance, Deng et al.",
    "(49) developed an explainable deep learning algorithm, DeepMSProfiler, which effectively removes batch effects by systematically excluding batch-related information through hidden layers.",
    "Building on this algorithm, the integration of metabolomics and methylation data in the study verified the associations between the PLA and UGT gene families and disease-specific metabolites.",
    "(50) revealed the drug resistance pathway in melanoma cells through single-cell multiomics analysis, providing a key and unique tool for addressing the signaling pathway function and metabolic changes in the adaptive development of drug resistance in tumor cells."
